    <p>
        - For the exothermic reaction, the energy of the products will be lower
        than the energy of the reactants, so the change in energy is negative.<br>
        - For the endothermic reaction, the energy of the products will be higher
        than the energy of the reactants, so the change in energy is positive.
    </p>
